About Us

The Mather Group is a Digital Marketing Agency with over 25 years in the space. We have worked with cyber security companies, warehouse juggernauts, media moguls, and everything in between. Founded by Josh Greene, who has spent between $1-5 million annually online for the last decade. We’ve managed online and DRTV programs for industry leaders such as Discovery Channel, Time Warner Cable, 1-800-PACK-RAT and Zipppy Shell, as well as helped a variety of smaller B2B and B2C businesses, and dramatically increased revenue everywhere. Josh has spoken at conferences ranging from the Mid Atlantic Marketing Summit to Search Engine Strategies to eTail.
                                      
